<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>FINV – Sobre</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: #07090d; color: #eef1f7;
      min-height: 100dvh; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    .topbar {
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
      display: flex; align-items: center;
      padding: 0 20px; height: 56px;
      background: rgba(7,9,13,.88);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid #1f2638;
    }
    .topbar-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
    .logo { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -.02em; }
    .btn-back {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
      padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: #8b94a8;
      border: 1px solid #1f2638; cursor: pointer;
      transition: color 150ms, border-color 150ms, background 150ms;
    }
    .btn-back:hover { color: #eef1f7; border-color: #2a3347; background: #111520; }
    .content {
      max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 24px 16px 48px;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px;
    }
    .card {
      background: #111520; border: 1px solid #1f2638;
      border-radius: 20px; padding: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.5);
    }
    .card-titulo {
      font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -.01em;
      margin-bottom: 20px; padding-bottom: 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid #1f2638;
    }
    .info-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1px; background: #1f2638;
      border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; margin-top: 16px;
    }
    .info-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; padding: 14px 16px; background: #0c0f16; }
    .info-label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .08em; color: #555e73; }
    .info-valor { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; }
    .membro-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; margin-top: 4px; }
    .membro-card {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
      gap: 8px; padding: 20px 12px;
      background: #0c0f16; border: 1px solid #1f2638;
      border-radius: 14px; text-align: center;
    }
    .membro-avatar {
      width: 64px; height: 64px; border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover; border: 2px solid #2a3347;
      background: #171c28;
    }
    .membro-nome  { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; }
    .membro-ra    { font-size: 12px; color: #555e73; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }
    .membro-papel {
      font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; color: #f59e0b;
      background: rgba(245,158,11,.12); border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.2);
      border-radius: 20px; padding: 3px 10px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .content { padding: 16px 12px 40px; }
      .card { padding: 18px 16px; }
      .info-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .membro-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 220px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="topbar">
    <div class="topbar-left">
      <a class="btn-back" href="/equipe-01/home">← Voltar</a>
      <span class="logo">Sobre</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <div class="card">
      <h3 class="card-titulo">Sobre o Projeto</h3>
      <p style="color:#a0a8b8;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:20px">
        O <strong>FINV</strong> é um simulador de financiamento de veículos desenvolvido
        para a disciplina de Gerência de Configuração, Entrega e Integração Contínua
        (GCEIC26) da Escola Politécnica da PUC-Campinas, 1º semestre de 2026.
      </p>

      <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="info-label">Disciplina</span>
          <span class="info-valor">GCEIC26</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="info-label">Professor</span>
          <span class="info-valor">Sérgio Marques</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="info-label">Semestre</span>
          <span class="info-valor">1S/2026</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="info-label">Stack</span>
          <span class="info-valor">Node.js + EJS</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 class="card-titulo">Nossa Equipe</h3>
      <div class="membro-grid">
        <div class="membro-card">
          <img class="membro-avatar" src="/equipe-01/Nonato.jpeg" alt="Felipe Nonato">
          <span class="membro-nome">Felipe Nonato</span>
          <span class="membro-ra">RA: 24021973</span>
          <span class="membro-papel">React App + Testes</span>
        </div>
        <div class="membro-card">
          <img class="membro-avatar" src="/equipe-01/Rafael.jpeg" alt="Rafael Pires">
          <span class="membro-nome">Rafael Pires</span>
          <span class="membro-ra">RA: 24007131</span>
          <span class="membro-papel">API + Testes</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
